            </row>
            <row id="771">
                <cell id="772"/>
            </row>
            <row id="773">
                <cell id="774">
                    <text id="520">
                        <property name="fontFamily">"Arial"</property>
                        <property name="contentType">auto</property>
                        <text-property name="content"><![CDATA[Dear Madam / Sir,

You are hereby notified that figure in our records a liability representing the invoices mentioned in the table attached to this.
 
We remind you that in accordance with Art. 1393 and 1396 Civil Code and your provider prior notification of the assignment of receivables, the Romanian Commercial Bank became the holder of the rights to your collection of amounts due under the contractual business relationship with the supplier of the above.

As mentioned in Appendix due invoices is outdated, please have available the payment of these invoices and account only for BCR indicated in the assignment specification that appears on every invoice issued by the supplier.

If you have already paid those bills, please ignore this letter.

For any further information or questions, please contact the ABC Bank

Thanks in advance for your cooperation.

Sincerely,


Executive Director, Head of Department,



Will submit Invoice attached (Annex)]]></text-property>
                    </text>
                </cell>
            </row>
